{"query": "SQLite WAL concurrent writer locking", "url": "https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WritableStreamDefaultWriter", "label": "irrelevant", "note": "hard-negative: the confirmed live false-positive (scored relevance:9 by phi4-mini)"}
{"query": "SQLite WAL concurrent writer locking", "url": "https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WritableStreamDefaultWriter/write", "label": "irrelevant", "note": "hard-negative: same MDN family, same confirmed live false-positive"}
{"query": "SQLite WAL concurrent writer locking", "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Banana", "label": "irrelevant", "note": "easy-negative sanity floor: failing this means broken, not just fooled"}

